    "created_at": "2015-06-05T20:10:47Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-06-05T20:10:47Z",
    "body": "IMO at least liblibc in its current form \u2013 trying to bind all platforms \u2013 should not exist at all and cargo should instead allow depending on different crates per-platform. I.e. you would depend on liblibc-gnu on GNU systems, liblibc-bsd on BSD, liblibc-apple on OS X, winapi packages on windows etc.\n",
